com.mot.rfid.api3

Class TAG_EVENT

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mot.rfid.api3.TAG_EVENT

  • public class TAG_EVENT
extends java.lang.Object
    TAG_EVENT specifies the event pertaining to a Tag reported via TAG_DATA.
